				<td colspan='2' class='diff-otitle'><div id="mw-diff-otitle1"><strong><a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Medak_Pocket&amp;oldid=619783444" title="Operation Medak Pocket">Revision as of 07:52, 4 August 2014</a> <span class="mw-diff-edit">(<a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Medak_Pocket&amp;action=edit&amp;oldid=619783444" title="Operation Medak Pocket">edit</a>)</span></strong></div><div id="mw-diff-otitle2"><a href="/wiki/User:Ohconfucius" title="User:Ohconfucius" class="mw-userlink">Ohconfucius</a> <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/wiki/User_talk:Ohconfucius" title="User talk:Ohconfucius">talk</a> | <a href="/wiki/Special:Contributions/Ohconfucius" title="Special:Contributions/Ohconfucius">contribs</a>)</span></div><div id="mw-diff-otitle3"> <span class="comment">(<a href="/wiki/User:Ohconfucius/script" title="User:Ohconfucius/script">Script</a>-assisted fixes: per <a href="/wiki/MOS:NUM" class="mw-redirect" title="MOS:NUM">MOS:NUM</a>, <a href="/wiki/MOS:CAPS" class="mw-redirect" title="MOS:CAPS">MOS:CAPS</a>, <a href="/wiki/MOS:LINK" class="mw-redirect" title="MOS:LINK">MOS:LINK</a>)</span></div><div id="mw-diff-otitle5"></div><div id="mw-diff-otitle4"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Operation_Medak_Pocket&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=619783444" title="Operation Medak Pocket" id="differences-prevlink">← Previous edit</a></div></td>
