<li id="cite_note-Windsor-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Windsor_8-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Windsor_8-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Windsor_8-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Windsor_8-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Windsor_8-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Windsor_8-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Windsor_8-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web">Lee A. Windsor. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://scholars.wlu.ca/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1087&amp;context=cmh">"The Medak Pocket"</a>. Ottawa, Canada: Conference of Defense Associations Institute<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">20 April</span> 2012</span>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOperation+Medak+Pocket&amp;rft.aulast=Lee+A.+Windsor&amp;rft.au=Lee+A.+Windsor&amp;rft.btitle=The+Medak+Pocket&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fscholars.wlu.ca%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D1087%26context%3Dcmh&amp;rft.place=Ottawa%2C+Canada&amp;rft.pub=Conference+of+Defense+Associations+Institute&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
